A process for preparing the copolymer according to any one of claims 16 to 21, comprising introducing the repeating unit (a1) having a structure represented by formula (a1-1) above in a side chain by reacting a polymer comprising:
(a0) a repeating unit having a structure represented by formula (a1-0) below in a side chain;
